channel.title: Need experienced person 508 portforwarding problem?
channel.description:
okay, so i have a netgear router, and everytime i try to portforward i get my friends to try and connect but they never can. i have a Sky Router Netgear DG834GT, and i just cannot get my server online, i have tried alot of things but it's just not happening. i have tried utorrent, but same thing- doesn't connect, yes i put the port as 43594, and my no-ip DUC is active but it's still not working. i can get it online on hamachi, but who wants a hamachi server? if you think you can help me please post below. i have been coding this alot lately and dont feel like making it a waste of time. if it helps, im using a client my friend uses to run his server off (508-ipchanger).
i have teamviewer if u could help or just reply here PLEASE!!, if you like i can give u staff position on my server if you help me fix this problem!!
